						<h1 class="title" id="page_title"> 15 U.S. Code § 45 - Unfair methods of competition unlawful; prevention by Commission </h1>
<div class="tabbable-panel">
<div class="tabbable-line">
<ul class="nav nav-tabs ">
<li class="active">
<a data-toggle="tab" href="#tab_default_1">
                        U.S. Code </a>
</li>
